org.universAAL.ui.dm.ui.preferences.buffer

Class UISubprofileInitializator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.universAAL.ui.dm.ui.preferences.buffer.UISubprofileInitializator

  • public class UISubprofileInitializator
extends Object
    Initializes UIPreferencesSubprofile based on stereotype data for AssistedPerson or Caregiver user and connects it with given User. Before that it checks if the User exists and if not adds it (to the Profiling server), it also checks if UserProfile exists for that UIRequest and if not it adds it and connects it with given User. In addition same initialization data is also stored in the UIPreferencesBuffer (although they are retrieved by periodic task triggered every predefined amount of time).
    Author:
    eandgrg
